<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ludwig XI., Friedrich III. und Ludwig XII., Grafen von Oettingen</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass die Nürnberger Kaufleute nicht zusammen an einem einzigen Tag, sondern je nach Bedarf zur Nördlinger Messe ziehen, und bittet um Verständnis und erneut um Geleit für Nürnberger Bürger und Kaufleute auf dem Weg zu und von der Messe.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_456" id="227r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_456_r1l16"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ludwıg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> den <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gebrüd<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_456_r1l17">vnd <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ludwıg<ex>en</ex></expan> dem <expan>Jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . grafen ʒu <expan>Ötınge<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_456_r1l18"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> als vns eẅr gnade <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat / daʒ Jr <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_456_r1l19">kawffleẅt Jr hab <expan>kawffmanſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> vnd dıe Jren <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> in <expan>Nördlıng<ex>er</ex></expan> markt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_456_r1l20">vnd <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> darawſʒ beleyten wellet / vnd eẅr gnade dabey <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_456_r1l21">wır mıt den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> beſtellen <expan>ſölte<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ ſıe auf <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> tag mıt eınander </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_456_r1l22">faren vnd ʒıehen ſölten etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_456_r1l23">wir daʒ etlıch dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> hınauf <expan>gecʒoge<ex>n</ex></expan> ſınd . ſo <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> etlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_456_r1l24">hernach hınauf ʒıehen vnd <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>yed<ex>er</ex>man</expan> nach ſeınr notdurft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_456_r1l25">als yeglıchs dink geſtalt ıſt / Alſo daʒ dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dar vnd dannen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_456_r1l26">ſamentlıch nıht faren noch <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> können / Als eẅr gnade ſelbs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_456_r1l27">auch wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> mag / <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr gnade mıt fleıſſ . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_456_r1l28">eẅr gnade <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> welle daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> Jr hab vnd dıe Jren ın den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_456_r1l29"><expan>nehſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Nördlıng<ex>er</ex></expan> markt vnd darawſʒ durch ewr <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rſchaft</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_456_r1l30">gepıete . <expan>ſıch<ex>er</ex></expan> geleytet <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . ſo ſıe vnd dıe Jren des begern </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_457" id="227v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l1">werden . als etc / das wellen etc . Vnd bıtten des eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l2">gnedıg <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> bey dıſem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l3">ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_456" id="227r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Ludwig<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> den <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>gebrüd<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Ludwig<ex>en</ex></expan> dem <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, Grafen
                        zu <expan>Ötinge<ex>n</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als uns ewr gnade
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, daz ir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt ir hab
                                <expan>kawffmansch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und die iren
                                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> in
                            <expan>Nördling<ex>er</ex></expan> markt und
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> darawsz beleyten wellet und ewr gnade
                        dabey <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan>, daz wir mit den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bestellen <expan>sölte<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        daz sie auf <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> tag miteinander faren und ziehen
                        sölten etc., das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> wir, daz etlich die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> hinauf <expan>geczoge<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sind, so <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> etlich hernach hinauf ziehen und
                                <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>yed<ex>er</ex>man</expan>
                        nach seinr notdurft, als yeglichs dink gestalt ist, also daz die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dar und dannen samentlich niht faren
                        noch <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> können, als ewr gnade selbs auch wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> mag. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr gnade mit fleiss, daz ewr gnade
                                <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan> welle, daz
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, ir hab und die iren in den
                                <expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Nördling<ex>er</ex></expan> markt und darawsz durch ewr
                                <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rschaft</expan> und gepiete
                            <expan>sich<ex>er</ex></expan> geleytet <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>,
                        so sie und die iren des begern <pb facs="#facs_457" id="227v"/>werden. Als etc. Das
                        wellen etc. Und bitten des ewr gnedig <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> bey disem <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
